. Jadrov\u233\'e9 elektr\u225\'e1rne s\u250\'fa v prev\u225\'e1dzke v \u244\'f4smich z p\u228\'e4tn\u225\'e1stich \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tov z Eur\u243\'f3pskej \u250\'fanie...}
